  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b86\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Recovery of the dead body of a man in an empty tomb",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A man's body has been recovered from Colombo's empty road. Police said the body has not yet been identified.",
        "It is noteworthy that the body of a 19-year-old youth was recovered from the same place a few days ago"
      ],
